highlights.text: “you and me eternal summer (feat. Jin Hwi PARK)” by Choi Yoon Young and jin hwi Park is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs South Korea, up 10 spots at #54.
Effie has the most spots on Viral Songs South Korea. “CAN I SIP 담배” is the highest at #3.
“PASSO BEM SOLTO - Slowed” by ATLXS has been on Viral Songs South Korea the longest, at 154 days straight.
